{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":418,"text":"When my father and I started a company"},{"time":3156,"text":"to 3D print human tissues and organs,"},{"time":6432,"text":"some people initially thought we were a little crazy."},{"time":9788,"text":"But since then, much progress has been made,"},{"time":12479,"text":"both in our lab and other labs around the world."},{"time":15686,"text":"And given this, we started getting questions like,"},{"time":18953,"text":"\"If you can grow human body parts,"},{"time":21680,"text":"can you also grow animal products like meat and leather?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27060,"text":"When someone first suggested this to me,"},{"time":29502,"text":"quite frankly I thought they were a little crazy,"},{"time":32456,"text":"but what I soon came to realize"},{"time":34559,"text":"was that this is not so crazy after all."},{"time":37805,"text":"What's crazy is what we do today."},{"time":40774,"text":"I'm convinced that in 30 years,"},{"time":42963,"text":"when we look back on today"},{"time":44685,"text":"and on how we raise and slaughter billions of animals"},{"time":48295,"text":"to make our hamburgers and our handbags,"},{"time":51198,"text":"we'll see this as being wasteful"},{"time":53380,"text":"and indeed crazy."},{"time":55670,"text":"Did you know that today we maintain"},{"time":58782,"text":"a global herd of 60 billion animals"},{"time":62123,"text":"to provide our meat, dairy, eggs and leather goods?"},{"time":67699,"text":"And over the next few decades,"},{"time":69769,"text":"as the world's population expands to 10 billion,"},{"time":72529,"text":"this will need to nearly double"},{"time":74174,"text":"to 100 billion animals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76759,"text":"But maintaining this herd"},{"time":78368,"text":"takes a major toll on our planet."},{"time":80667,"text":"Animals are not just raw materials."},{"time":84286,"text":"They're living beings,"},{"time":85909,"text":"and already our livestock"},{"time":87827,"text":"is one of the largest users of land,"},{"time":90406,"text":"fresh water,"},{"time":91758,"text":"and one of the biggest producers of greenhouse gases"},{"time":94491,"text":"which drive climate change."},{"time":96120,"text":"On top of this,"},{"time":97450,"text":"when you get so many animals so close together,"},{"time":100674,"text":"it creates a breeding ground for disease"},{"time":103144,"text":"and opportunities for harm and abuse."},{"time":106727,"text":"Clearly, we cannot continue on this path"},{"time":109257,"text":"which puts the environment, public health,"},{"time":113080,"text":"and food security at risk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115522,"text":"There is another way, because essentially,"},{"time":119088,"text":"animal products are just collections of tissues,"},{"time":123374,"text":"and right now we breed and raise"},{"time":125798,"text":"highly complex animals"},{"time":127727,"text":"only to create products"},{"time":129418,"text":"that are made of relatively simple tissues."},{"time":132133,"text":"What if, instead of starting with a complex"},{"time":135343,"text":"and sentient animal,"},{"time":137465,"text":"we started with what the tissues are made of,"},{"time":141013,"text":"the basic unit of life,"},{"time":143559,"text":"the cell?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":146040,"text":"This is biofabrication, where cells themselves"},{"time":149760,"text":"can be used to grow biological products"},{"time":152386,"text":"like tissues and organs."},{"time":154278,"text":"Already in medicine,"},{"time":155976,"text":"biofabrication techniques have been used"},{"time":158179,"text":"to grow sophisticated body parts,"},{"time":160615,"text":"like ears, windpipes, skin, blood vessels and bone,"},{"time":165513,"text":"that have been successfully implanted into patients."},{"time":168747,"text":"And beyond medicine, biofabrication can be"},{"time":172855,"text":"a humane, sustainable and scalable new industry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177621,"text":"And we should begin by reimagining leather."},{"time":183431,"text":"I emphasize leather because it is so widely used."},{"time":187701,"text":"It is beautiful, and it has long been a part of our history."},{"time":192604,"text":"Growing leather is also technically simpler"},{"time":194505,"text":"than growing other animal products like meat."},{"time":197280,"text":"It mainly uses one cell type,"},{"time":199390,"text":"and it is largely two-dimensional."},{"time":202515,"text":"It is also less polarizing for consumers and regulators."},{"time":206683,"text":"Until biofabrication is better understood,"},{"time":209781,"text":"it is clear that, initially at least,"},{"time":211966,"text":"more people would be willing to wear novel materials"},{"time":216017,"text":"than would be willing to eat novel foods,"},{"time":218652,"text":"no matter how delicious."},{"time":220603,"text":"In this sense, leather is a gateway material,"},{"time":223710,"text":"a beginning for the mainstream biofabrication industry."},{"time":228782,"text":"If we can succeed here,"},{"time":230666,"text":"it brings our other consumer bioproducts like meat"},{"time":233942,"text":"closer on the horizon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236706,"text":"Now how do we do it?"},{"time":239171,"text":"To grow leather, we begin by taking cells"},{"time":242443,"text":"from an animal, through a simple biopsy."},{"time":245275,"text":"The animal could be a cow,"},{"time":247283,"text":"lamb, or even something more exotic."},{"time":249980,"text":"This process does no harm,"},{"time":252032,"text":"and Daisy the cow can live a happy life."},{"time":254934,"text":"We then isolate the skin cells"},{"time":256669,"text":"and multiply them in a cell culture medium."},{"time":259538,"text":"This takes millions of cells"},{"time":260711,"text":"and expands them into billions."},{"time":263830,"text":"And we then coax these cells to produce collagen,"},{"time":266444,"text":"as they would naturally."},{"time":267871,"text":"This collagen is the stuff between cells."},{"time":270200,"text":"It's natural connective tissue."},{"time":272693,"text":"It's the extracellular matrix,"},{"time":274253,"text":"but in leather, it's the main building block."},{"time":277462,"text":"And what we next do is we take the cells and their collagen"},{"time":281175,"text":"and we spread them out to form sheets,"},{"time":283152,"text":"and then we layer these thin sheets on top of one another,"},{"time":286594,"text":"like phyllo pastry, to form thicker sheets,"},{"time":290123,"text":"which we then let mature."},{"time":291977,"text":"And finally, we take this multilayered skin"},{"time":295189,"text":"and through a shorter and much less chemical tanning process,"},{"time":299112,"text":"we create leather."},{"time":301288,"text":"And so I'm very excited to show you,"},{"time":303482,"text":"for the first time,"},{"time":305631,"text":"the first batch of our cultured leather,"},{"time":309641,"text":"fresh from the lab."},{"time":311204,"text":"This is real, genuine leather,"},{"time":314783,"text":"without the animal sacrifice."},{"time":318306,"text":"It can have all the characteristics of leather"},{"time":321484,"text":"because it is made of the same cells,"},{"time":324969,"text":"and better yet,"},{"time":326918,"text":"there is no hair to remove,"},{"time":330793,"text":"no scars or insect's bites,"},{"time":333326,"text":"and no waste."},{"time":334766,"text":"This leather can be grown in the shape of a wallet,"},{"time":338190,"text":"a handbag or a car seat."},{"time":341276,"text":"It is not limited to the irregular shape of a cow"},{"time":344492,"text":"or an alligator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347322,"text":"And because we make this material,"},{"time":349876,"text":"we grow this leather from the ground up,"},{"time":352158,"text":"we can control its properties in very interesting ways."},{"time":355191,"text":"This piece of leather"},{"time":357726,"text":"is a mere seven tissue layers thick,"},{"time":361244,"text":"and as you can see, it is nearly transparent."},{"time":365047,"text":"And this leather is 21 layers thick and quite opaque."},{"time":374214,"text":"You don't have that kind of fine control"},{"time":377224,"text":"with conventional leather."},{"time":379513,"text":"And we can tune this leather for other desirable qualities,"},{"time":382758,"text":"like softness, breathability,"},{"time":386523,"text":"durability, elasticity and even things like pattern."},{"time":391720,"text":"We can mimic nature,"},{"time":393891,"text":"but in some ways also improve upon it."},{"time":397179,"text":"This type of leather can do what today's leather does,"},{"time":401177,"text":"but with imagination, probably much more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404618,"text":"What could the future of animal products look like?"},{"time":408847,"text":"It need not look like this,"},{"time":411206,"text":"which is actually the state of the art today."},{"time":413939,"text":"Rather, it could be much more like this."},{"time":416931,"text":"Already, we have been manufacturing with cell cultures"},{"time":419164,"text":"for thousands of years, beginning with products"},{"time":421929,"text":"like wine, beer and yogurt."},{"time":424558,"text":"And speaking of food, our cultured food has evolved,"},{"time":427892,"text":"and today we prepare cultured food"},{"time":430153,"text":"in beautiful, sterile facilities like this."},{"time":432471,"text":"A brewery is essentially a bioreactor."},{"time":435671,"text":"It is where cell culture takes place."},{"time":438440,"text":"Imagine that in this facility,"},{"time":440985,"text":"instead of brewing beer,"},{"time":442731,"text":"we were brewing leather"},{"time":445312,"text":"or meat."},{"time":448009,"text":"Imagine touring this facility,"},{"time":450654,"text":"learning about how the leather or meat is cultured,"},{"time":454385,"text":"seeing the process from beginning to end,"},{"time":457146,"text":"and even trying some."},{"time":458542,"text":"It's clean, open and educational,"},{"time":461648,"text":"and this is in contrast to the hidden,"},{"time":464068,"text":"guarded and remote factories"},{"time":466146,"text":"where leather and meat is produced today."},{"time":469627,"text":"Perhaps biofabrication"},{"time":472454,"text":"is a natural evolution of manufacturing for mankind."},{"time":476734,"text":"It's environmentally responsible,"},{"time":479187,"text":"efficient and humane."},{"time":482349,"text":"It allows us to be creative."},{"time":484543,"text":"We can design new materials, new products,"},{"time":487763,"text":"and new facilities."},{"time":490962,"text":"We need to move past just killing animals"},{"time":494802,"text":"as a resource"},{"time":496635,"text":"to something more civilized and evolved."},{"time":502556,"text":"Perhaps we are ready for something"},{"time":505241,"text":"literally and figuratively more cultured."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510826,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512207,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}